            <title>[CASSANDRA-18303] Feature documentation lost / moved out of focus</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-18303</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Documentation added with&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17344&quot; title=&quot;Documentation update of virtual table system_views.clients&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17344&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17344&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; wasn&apos;t moved with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17976&quot; title=&quot;WEBSITE - Update What&amp;#39;s New Page for 4.1 and trunk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17976&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17976&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and now the documentation on the website page &quot;Cassandra/Operating/Virtual tables&quot; shows an outdated version for &lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/4.1/cassandra/operating/virtualtables.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;4.1&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/operating/virtualtables.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;latest&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
